{
  "texts": [
    "With a voluminous scale exceeding 2.4M entries, each instance originates from genuine short texts composed by users of Sina Weibo, each supplemented with a succinct summary.",
    "Social media textual content exhibits traits such as brevity, a broad spectrum of language styles, and heightened levels of noise.",
    "• MediaSum (Zhu et al, 2021).",
    "In contrast to other text summarization datasets, which rely on news articles, the MediaSum dataset pivots towards the realm of media interviews.",
    "The creators have curated interview transcripts sourced from NPR and CNN, utilizing summaries and topic descriptions as abstracts."
  ]
}